06:59.169 --> 07:01.713
Perry the Platypus, did you
get yourself upholstered?

07:03.214 --> 07:04.799
Yay!
Whoa!

07:04.799 --> 07:06.468
Oh, man!

07:06.468 --> 07:08.678
Actually, this is
way too tame.

07:08.678 --> 07:11.097
Hey! Crank it up to
double black diamond!

07:11.097 --> 07:12.474
Yeah!
Whoo-hoo!

07:14.559 --> 07:16.936
This parachute
smells funny.

07:22.484 --> 07:24.861
Nice re-purposing of Buford's
chewed gum collection!

07:24.861 --> 07:26.488
Whoo-hoo!

07:26.488 --> 07:29.240
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

07:29.240 --> 07:30.742
Whoo-hoo!

07:32.994 --> 07:34.579
That sure was great.

07:34.579 --> 07:36.247
But I wish Perry
was here for once.

07:36.247 --> 07:37.832
He would just love it!

07:38.750 --> 07:39.959
I do love it!

07:39.959 --> 07:41.628
I've never had
so much fun!

07:41.628 --> 07:44.005
Anyway, fellas,
I'm gonna hit the road.

07:44.005 --> 07:48.635
Well, he's no platypus,
but still a lovely fellow.

07:48.635 --> 07:51.846
You know, maybe I should've thought
before blurring my own vision!

07:51.846 --> 07:53.765
It was very
short-sighted of me.

07:53.765 --> 07:56.643
Hey, can you make that
digga-digga-digga-digga-digga sound for me...

07:56.643 --> 07:59.020
(GRUNTS) That was a
lucky kick, Perry...

07:59.020 --> 08:00.730
(YELLING)

08:00.730 --> 08:02.899
Wait! I just need to
blast myself again,

08:02.899 --> 08:06.027
and I'll clear my vision
and get the jump on him!

08:06.027 --> 08:07.529
(GROANS)

08:07.529 --> 08:09.155
Hey, hey,
YOU jumped on me!

08:09.155 --> 08:11.991
You used my own turn
of phrase against me.

08:11.991 --> 08:13.284
Wow, irony.

08:13.284 --> 08:14.536
(CLATTERING)

08:14.536 --> 08:16.663
Really?
A stack of buckets?

08:16.663 --> 08:20.291
That'll teach me to randomly stack
buckets in the center of my lab.

08:20.291 --> 08:22.252
Oh! Another reject.

08:22.252 --> 08:23.795
Here you go, Perry.

08:23.795 --> 08:26.548
Oh, there you are! What
are you doing up there?

08:26.548 --> 08:28.925
Oh, it's a bag of bread.
(CHUCKLES)

08:28.925 --> 08:31.553
I've been up so long,
I'm starting to see things.

08:37.892 --> 08:43.063
<i>P Three point one four
